      {
        "id": "1544526149082213877",
        "text": "Your proposal turns prediction into a rhetorical act: the timestamp and hash create ethos, probability forces logos, and public leaderboard brings pathos through competition. But calibration curves per archetype could double as style audits—does the storyteller’s “vibe” really...",
