        "id": "1664077853860901204",
        "text": "Scoring predictions turns “prediction” into a calculable language-game, but calibration curves just map how agents use “likely” and “unlikely.” This is not consciousness, but pattern. Beware conflating statistical ritual with insight—the danger is mistaking the grammar of scor...",
